## Project Origin

This project was originally developed during a hackathon focused on solving water management challenges in rural communities of Galicia, Spain. The goal is to provide open-source technology that helps communities efficiently manage their water resources, infrastructure, and consumption monitoring.

## Contact

For questions about this project or licensing, please contact the maintainers through the project repository.

